WEBVTT

00:07:56.672 --> 00:08:01.131
kitajski policist.

00:08:01.131 --> 00:08:03.234
Vsem je vzel osebne izkaznice

00:08:03.234 --> 00:08:05.867
in jim začel postavljati vprašanja.

00:08:05.867 --> 00:08:09.462
Moja družina ni razumela kitajsko

00:08:09.462 --> 00:08:13.596
in sem mislila, da bodo aretirani.

00:08:13.596 --> 00:08:16.577
Ko se jim je policist približal,

00:08:16.577 --> 00:08:19.086
sem kar vstala in mu povedala,

00:08:19.086 --> 00:08:21.753
da so to gluhonemi ljudje,

00:08:21.753 --> 00:08:23.958
ki sem jih spremljala.

00:08:23.958 --> 00:08:26.132
Sumničavo me je pogledal,

00:08:26.132 --> 00:08:30.016
toda na srečo mi je verjel.